@node MAIN "corners_plugin: Introduction"


    @{b}corners_plugin@{ub}

        by @{b}Ali Graham@{ub} <agraham@hal9000.net.au>



    @{b}corners_plugin@{ub} is a PLUGIN which enables you to choose
    between the four corners of a square (envisaged usage;
    screen blanker preferences program). While maybe not
    immediately useful to the general public, it illustrates
    the usage of detecting input in different areas of a
    PLUGIN.

